We’re attempting to use Sysid to characterize our robot, but when we deploy the characterization code the robot throws the following errors then crashes.

FATAL ERROR: HAL could not be initialized
Failed to read Watchdog status from FPGA: -61200

This is with wpilib 2023 on both the roboRIO and two different laptops. It persists after a robot reboot.

Any ideas for how to troubleshoot this?
